re_item_assets/steam/apps/3269670/extras/6b1913b895dfd0679849df0960c7c866.avif?t=1741634662\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269670/extras_big/6b1913b895dfd0679849df0960c7c866.avif?t=1741634662 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269670/extras/2e75269e47d0563e851bc07808de07e5.avif?t=1741634662\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269670/extras_big/2e75269e47d0563e851bc07808de07e5.avif?t=1741634662 width=800 height=450 /></span><strong>Welcome to The Pirate's Casino!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the land of pirates, you embark on an adventure in a casino full of risks, floating in the middle of the sea. Play various casino games on the ship, increase your gold, take risks, and grow your fortune. Use your winnings to purchase challenging parkour missions, overcome obstacles, find treasures, and add to your pirate fortune!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Casino Games:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BlackJack</strong>: Try your luck at the Blackjack table, prepared according to the general rules of the world, and seize the opportunity to win.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roulette</strong>: It's hard to predict where the ball will land, but if you trust your luck, don't miss this game!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Case Opening</strong>: Open chance-based boxes to win big rewards. Each box is filled with completely random prizes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Up & Down</strong>: Bet on the next playing card and take the risk to double your winnings.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Slot Game</strong>: Spin the slot machine and match at least 8 of the same items to win. Watching your luck unfold will be very exciting!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Parkour Game:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to the mermaid NPC to take on parkour missions and purchase these challenging tasks with gold. Once you complete the parkour, a treasure worth much more than what you paid will be waiting for you!</p>",
